<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>18Day - The Habit Launchpad</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4361EE;
            --primary-dark: #3A0CA3;
            --accent: #F72585;
            --light: #F8F9FA;
            --dark: #212529;
            --success: #4CC9F0;
            --gray: #6C757D;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .logo p {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .card-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .card-header h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .card-header p {
            color: var(--gray);
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #DDE2E5;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(67, 97, 238, 0.25);
            outline: none;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
        }
        
        .info-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        .info-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
        }
        
        .info-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .day-progress {
            display: flex;
            margin: 30px 0;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .day {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #E9ECEF;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--dark);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .day.active {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(67, 97, 238, 0.25);
        }
        
        .day.critical {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .day:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #E9ECEF;
            width: 100%;
            left: 100%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .day:last-child:after {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .progress-label {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray);
        }
        
        .brain-visual {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .brain-graphic {
            width: 200px;
            height: 150px;
            background-color: #F8F9FA;
            border-radius: 100px 100px 60px 60px;
            position: relative;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 2px solid #DEE2E6;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .neural-path {
            position: absolute;
            height: 4px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .path-1 {
            width: 30px;
            background-color: var(--success);
            top: 40px;
            left: 40px;
            transform: rotate(30deg);
        }
        
        .path-2 {
            width: 60px;
            background-color: var(--success);
            top: 70px;
            left: 60px;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }
        
        .path-3 {
            width: 80px;
            background-color: var(--success);
            top: 100px;
            left: 50px;
            transform: rotate(20deg);
        }
        
        .path-4 {
            width: 40px;
            background-color: var(--success);
            top: 50px;
            right: 50px;
            transform: rotate(-40deg);
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>18Day</h1>
            <p>The Habit Launchpad</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>Start Your 18-Day Habit Journey</h2>
                <p>Just 18 days to build a neural pathway that lasts a lifetime.</p>
            </div>
            
            <form action="/challenge/create" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="habitName">What habit do you want to build?</label>
                    <input type="text" id="habitName" name="habitDescription" class="form-control" placeholder="e.g., Morning meditation, Daily reading" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="userEmail">Your email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="userEmail" name="initiatorEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="friendEmail">Accountability partner's email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="friendEmail" name="friendEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="friend@example.com" required>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Launch My 18-Day Challenge</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-section">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Why 18 Days Works</h3>
                <p>Research shows 18 days is the minimum time needed to form a simple habit. Get through this critical window, and your brain takes over from there.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Critical Formation Period</h3>
                <div class="day-progress">
                    <div class="day critical">1</div>
                    <div class="day critical">6</div>
                    <div class="day critical">12</div>
                    <div class="day critical">18</div>
                    <div class="day">30</div>
                </div>
                <div class="progress-label">
                    <span>Start</span>
                    <span>Critical Period</span>
                    <span>Automatic</span>
                </div>
                <p>The first 18 days show the steepest improvement in automaticity. We focus on this critical period when your brain forms new neural pathways.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Your Brain on Habits</h3>
                <div class="brain-visual">
                    <div class="brain-graphic">
                        <div class="neural-path path-1"></div>
                        <div class="neural-path path-2"></div>
                        <div class="neural-path path-3"></div>
                        <div class="neural-path path-4"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>After consistent practice, your brain creates strong neural pathways. What was once difficult becomes your brain's default mode.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Based on habit formation research by Phillippa Lally et al., UCL</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>